code:
stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> Idle
  Idle --> Processing : start
  state Processing {
    [*] --> Parse
    Parse --> Validate
    state Validate {
      [*] --> Check
      Check --> [*]
    }
    Validate --> Decision
    state Decision <<choice>>
    Decision --> Success : ok
    Decision --> Error : fail
  }
  Error --> Idle : reset
  Success --> Idle : restart
  Success --> [*] : finish
